targettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> listed are for the labelled, declared <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_bd00c79b-cca8-40ff-b702-cd244bedf3f5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of insulation.</li><li id="_ca8f6322-130d-40be-ae43-376d2881dbda">X = not permitted.</li><li id="_5238173d-94c1-4094-b48f-1aa5df2cc725">This Table shows wall heights for single <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_0e8d6d89-66d1-44be-8993-7536fa8069f1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> dwellings. For two <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_d1b7daf3-346d-4834-88da-53527277c48c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> (or more) dwellings, add R0.5 to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_ba898038-ab9c-4379-9a57-e3bdbf3682ac" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> given in this Table.</li><li id="_8fcb6bcc-54c5-42ee-90b4-ceb9cb64ac75">Where an overhang of &gt; 1500 mm is used, the values for &gt; 1200 to ≤ 1500 apply provided no more than 15% of the total opaque wall area of the dwelling (excluding windows/doors) is covered by overhangs &gt; 1500 mm.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>